description:
he AMD Ryzen Z2 Extreme is set to redefine handheld gaming! 🔥 In this video, we analyze the predicted performance of this powerful new chip.  Featuring 8 cores and 16 threads based on the Zen 5 architecture, along with a 16CU RDNA 3.5 iGPU, the Z2 Extreme is essentially a more efficient version of the Ryzen AI 9 HX 370.  We discuss its potential impact on devices like the Lenovo Legion GO 2 and speculate on future releases, including possible contenders from ASUS such as the ROG Ally 2 or a higher-end ROG Ally X 2 Pro.  Will this be the next big thing in portable gaming? Watch now to find out!  #AMD #RyzenZ2Extreme #HandheldGaming #LenovoLegionGO #ASUSROGAlly #ROGAlly2 #GamingPC #PortableGaming #TechReview #NewTech
